Kingsley Academy (formerly Hounslow Manor Community School) is a secondary school incorporating a sixth form since its conversion to an academy in April 2013. The school has been sponsored by the London Academies Enterprise Trust (LAET), a subsidiary company of the Academies Enterprise Trust (AET).
Kingsley Academy also secured Â£29m for a new school building with construction work beginning in the spring of 2016. The capacity of the school is set to increase to 1,400 from approximately 850.
